CatDescriptText: Cutline of related image published in Pittsburgh Courier newspaper, June 15, 1963, pg. 15, reads: "The 1963 Courier-WAMO Home-A-Rama. Pittsburgh's only home and food show, opened before a huge throng last Thursday, June 6, at the spacious Syria Mosque in Oakland..."
